widgets.name: Text
widgets.textContent: The purpose of this page is to give the audience an idea of the type of actions and frequency users have with Datameer.  If a high percentage of Authentication action is visible, that could mean either someone doing lots of operations via Rest API for example.  Another example, a high JOB type and low FILESYSTEM activity can indicate that there is not a whole lot activity in Datameer Filesystem (adding folders, adding/modifying workbooks, etc).
